title: PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs
text: > Top News PHOTO GALLERY: Daniel Murphy's 7 postseason home runs FILE - At left, in this Oct. 9, 2015, file photo, New York Mets' Daniel Murphy watches his first 2015 postseason home run, against the Los Angeles Dodgers during the fourth inning in Game 1 of baseball's National League Division Series in Los Angeles. At right, also in an Oct. 9, 2015, file photo, Mets' Daniel Murphy celebrates his solo home run as Dodgers catcher A.J. Ellis looks down during the fourth inning in Game 1 of baseball's National League Division Series in Los Angeles. Murphy won NL Championship Series MVP on Wednesday night, Oct. 21, 2015, after homering for a postseason-record sixth straight game, leading the Mets over the Chicago Cubs 8-3 to complete a four-game sweep. (AP Photo/File)
